{"id":22204,"title":"Crimean-Congo hemorrhagic fever among health care workers, Turkey.","abstract":"We investigated 9 cases of Crimean-Congo hemorrhagic fever (1 fatal, 2 asymptomatic) among health care workers in Turkey. Needlestick injuries were reported for 4 workers. Eight received ribavirin. In addition to standard precautions, airborne infection isolation precautions are essential during aerosol-generating procedures. For postexposure prophylaxis and therapy, ribavirin should be given. ","date":"2014-02-25","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24564994","annotations":[{"name":"Infection","weight":0.752214,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Bleeding","weight":0.740234,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bleeding"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.736795,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.710086,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Fever","weight":0.601684,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fever"},{"name":"Turkey","weight":0.561754,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turkey"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.27754,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Post-exposure prophylaxis","weight":0.223912,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Post-exposure_prophylaxis"},{"name":"Prophylaxis","weight":0.17916,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prophylaxis"},{"name":"Asymptomatic","weight":0.151091,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asymptomatic"},{"name":"Ribavirin","weight":0.124145,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ribavirin"},{"name":"Solitude","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solitude"},{"name":"Standardization","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standardization"},{"name":"Airborne forces","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Airborne_forces"},{"name":"Viral hemorrhagic fever","weight":0.0163827,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Viral_hemorrhagic_fever"}]}
